  "title": "SITE ENGINEER",
  "description": "<h2>About Us</h2><p>Bhuvan Construction Pte Ltd is a growing construction firm in Singapore, known for delivering high-quality building and infrastructure projects. As we expand, we are looking for a skilled Site Engineer to join our dynamic and committed team.</p><p><strong>Roles & Responsibilities</strong></p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li> Supervise daily site operations to ensure adherence to safety and quality standards.  </li></ul><ul><li> Coordinate with various teams to ensure the timely delivery of materials and resources.</li></ul><ul><li>Maintain accurate documentation of site activities and progress reports.</li></ul><ul><li>Identify potential risks and implement mitigation strategies to maintain project timelines.</li></ul><ul><li>Ensure compliance with applicable codes, standards, and safety regulations</li></ul><ul><li>Liaise with subcontractors, and suppliers to resolve technical, site issues coordinate site activities</li></ul><ul><li>Monitor project progress, quality, cost, and timelines , Master programs and construction schedules using MS Project, Review and interpret tender documents, construction drawing, specifications and contracts  </li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li> Diploma or bachelor’s degree in civil engineering, or a related field</li></ul><ul><li> Minimum 5 years of construction experience</li></ul><ul><li>NRP Linkway Experience required </li></ul><ul><li>Knowledge of site safety regulations. </li></ul><ul><li>Proficiency in construction software (AutoCAD)</li></ul><ul><li> Able to workday or night shift</li></ul><ul><li>Willing to work 6 days</li></ul>",
